data.description: This charming and inviting home has three spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms, plus a spacious, private yard for entertaining. The attached garage provides convenience and protection for your vehicles, while the covered back deck offers a perfect spot to unwind and enjoy the picturesque views of the beautifully landscaped yard. This home has seen numerous updates, blending functionality and aesthetics, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a delightful and comfortable home in Sturgis, South Dakota. With a 3.5% assumable loan, call to find out how you can make this wonderful opportunity your own.
